    "This complexity poses a challenge in understanding the skin-friction drag across diverse scales.",
    "To demonstrate the model's capability in capturing the multiscale drag characteristic, we present in figure 15 the one-dimensional spectrum of surface tangential stress relative to wavelength, averaged across all instantaneous waves, for the high wind speed condition of W1-14 (interpolation dataset with a wind speed of 14.82 m s -1).",
    "A solid black line represents the spectrum derived from experimental measurements, while the model's prediction is indicated by a dashed line.",
    "It should be noted here that the experimental spectrum shown in this figure is based on the filtered raw data, as explained in § 2.2.1.",
    "A visual examination of these spectra offers compelling evidence that the CNN model's predictions align remarkably well with the experimental reference data."
